snippet.title: RPG Fairy Elements - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What awaits at the end of an adventure that spans over 200 years?
RPG Fairy Elements is now available for Android!

Download it from Google Play
Premium: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.fairyelementspremium&hl=en
Freemium: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.fairyelements&hl=en

Yamato is a royal knight, fighting to protect the peace of his kingdom. His sword is imbued with the mysterious power of Material. However, in the battle, he was somehow transported to a world 200 years in the future...

©2016 KEMCO/EXE-CREATE
